scene.message:
Kandori: Hmph.{nl}
Youth sometimes destroys{nl}
itself...{waitkey}A common mistake for{nl}
those who overrate{nl}
their own strength.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Aki!{nl}
That's not your papa!{nl}
You know that, don't you?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, mister!{nl}
Give back the compact!{nl}
Ayase's gonna borrow it!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: This is the form{nl}
of my ambition...{wait_fr:79}{nl}
Behold its power!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Don't call your{nl}
elder brother's name so{nl}
freely. Filthy bastard{nl}
though you are,{waitkey}{clearbox}the same Kandori blood{nl}
runs in you. Mind your{nl}
tongue...{wait_fr:79} though it's futile.{nl}
A stray's pup is a stray.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Shut up!!{wait_fr:60}{nl}
I'm a Kido!{nl}
I'm Reiji Kido!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Toyed with by your father,{nl}
thrown out like an old rag -{nl}
my mother's bitterness!!{waitkey}This scar hasn't forgotten{nl}
a thing!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Hmph... how dull.{nl}
Go take it up with our{nl}
dead father's grave.{waitkey}{ret}
